	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You manage to wield some kind of authority over fire, making you a Baron of fire. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Constitution score increases by 1.</p></li><li><p>You gain an @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.TkUBkWa7Ltfsmm0y]{Edict of Flame} of your choice. You can launch this edict once per Long Rest.</p></li><li><p>A number of times equal to your proficiency bonus per Short Rest, when you hit a creature, you can inflict additional fire damage equal to your Constitution Modifier.</p></li></ul>",
